cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use TorchKM in your research, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "TorchKM: Fast Kernel Machines in PyTorch"
abstract: >-
  TorchKM is a GPU-accelerated PyTorch library for kernel machines.
  It provides kernel classifiers (SVM, DWD, logistic), kernel quantile
  regression, Nyström approximations of each, integrated cross-validated
  model selection over a regularization path, and a scikit-learn-style
  Python API.
authors:
